{"tid":1599617,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發：俞懷松於Twitter轉發《10.1光復香港宣言》表示支持】","createTime":"2019-09-28T06:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T06:02:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6d72d1dd9f7229166925de6b8b51a907357f1e31","tid":1599617,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:06:05.000Z","msg":"美國共和黨海外事務組織副主席俞懷松（Solomon Yue）在今天稍早時分於Twitter轉發一篇由香港網民自發編寫的《己亥年十月一日光復香港宣言 》，並表示美國會一直與香港人同行。<br />\n<br />\n撰寫宣言的文宣組網民於連登討論區指出，《10.1光復香港宣言》的意義重大：<br />\n<br />\n「普羅大眾以至國際社會或未能明白，我們堅持抗爭嘅原因。在十月一日此重要日子，我們更應以一份宣言，係抗爭現場向全世界再次表明我們嘅訴求和堅持。」<br />\n<br />\n他們更希望此宣言能令社會理解行動升級背後之原因，並為未來的政治藍圖作出論述補充。<br />\n<br />\n俞懷松的推文（歡迎瘋狂RT！）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/solomonyue/status/1177586710567219200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolomonyue%2Fstatus%2F1177586710567219200&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj5hvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=afe2b33d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolomonyue%2Fstatus%2F1177586710567219200&h=668a9ba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/solomonyue/status/1177586710567219200</a><br />\n<br />\n宣言原文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1595334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1595334</a>"},{"pid":"7240cfafc7425d1deb870cd47be13f1d4d4a9e57","tid":1599617,"uid":125542,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"佢真係跟得好貼 一直企係香港呢邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f10e0fc66dfa08cbc1fb53097c094e6d5961c9","tid":1599617,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:12:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14bdb686f796d149c370d7d5a8804075a9f0b8cc","tid":1599617,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"289bbd87bfb35c5501018d7a07ec5c2f21aff31f","tid":1599617,"uid":184366,"like":